People want to get more in exchange for their most least. The world wants to get the best in exchange for the smallest cost they could pay. This is absolutely insane and out of proportion. Are you willing to give your 100% today? .
Be planted in this moment of time, give your 100%. When you are in a meeting with your team, listen 100%, participate 100%. If you are editing a video be there 100%. If you are spending time with your family, kids, or siblings, or date with you special someone, be there 100% heart and mind and soul. Look them in the eyes. Appreciate the moment. Whatever you are doing passionately, the minimum requirements of passion dosage must at least be 100%.
.
That’s it, I talked to you, I put my heart into this. I talked to myself for today. Now let’s do it. Make it a religion, make it your happy moments. That is the happiest moment of your life when you are on your 100%.
